### Create Customer
POST https://localhost:7xxx/api/customer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@email.com",
  "phone": "+1234567890"
}

### Get All Customers
GET https://localhost:7xxx/api/customer

### Create Account
POST https://localhost:7xxx/api/account
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "{{customerId}}",
  "initialBalance": 1000.00,
  "accountType": "Savings"
}

### Get All Accounts
GET https://localhost:7xxx/api/account

### Transfer Money
POST https://localhost:7xxx/api/transaction/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccountNumber": "{{fromAccountNumber}}",
  "toAccountNumber": "{{toAccountNumber}}",
  "amount": 250.00,
  "description": "Payment for services"
}

### Get Transaction History
GET https://localhost:7xxx/api/transaction/history/{{accountId}}?page=1&pageSize=10